Homepage: https://github.com/yasunorioi/ntripcaster
Description: NTRIP Caster for OpenWRT — GNSS RTK correction data server
 Zero-dependency static binary. Streams RTCM3 from base stations to rovers.
 Compatible with u-blox ZED-F9P, Trimble, Leica, and any NTRIP v1 client.
